abstract: In a new television commercial, Ron Paul, a former obstetrician, is reminding conservative voters in Iowa of his antiabortion credentials.
snippet: In a new television commercial, Ron Paul, a former obstetrician, is reminding conservative voters in Iowa of his antiabortion credentials.
lead_paragraph: Ron Paul is best known for his antigovernment crusades and his rebukes of the Federal Reserve.

headline.main: New Paul Ad in Iowa Focuses on Abortion
